// NYSE details
=== INTRO_300 ===
# id: INTRO_300
# mode: day
~ set_header("Diner, Bank Street, Ottawa", "Monday morning")
Robert turns his coffee mug a quarter rotation.  He does this when he's choosing his words.
"Influence patterns," he says.  "Members who've been attending regularly show progressive changes in behaviour and personality.  Not sudden — gradual.  Each step looks like a natural extension of the one before it.  A person who was relatively conservative six months ago is now doing things they wouldn't have imagined a year prior."
Another pause.  "Ass fisting," he says dryly.
You raise an eyebrow.  He almost grins.  He's giving you shit.
"The escalation is the signature."
* [Continue] -> INTRO_305

// NYSE continued
